Reasoning: The paper deals with decoding of bit interleaved coded modulation (BICM) applied to both multiband and MIMO OFDM systems under imperfect channel state information. This involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), communication systems (cs.COMM), signal processing (cs.SI), networked systems (cs.NI), and multimedia (cs.MM).
